WEBVTT

00:00:28.829 --> 00:00:32.506
=Love Lurking=

00:00:32.541 --> 00:00:33.696
=Episode 18=

00:00:34.464 --> 00:00:35.159
Are you okay?

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:37.799
Are you hurt?

00:00:48.159 --> 00:00:49.600
Should I call you K

00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:52.280
or Song Qian?

00:00:55.232 --> 00:00:56.384
What are you talking about?

00:01:01.439 --> 00:01:03.759
I pressed it
when I was in danger just now.

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:07.519
The person who knew I was in danger
and would come to save me

00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:09.439
would only be K.

00:01:09.760 --> 00:01:10.799
Because you said,

00:01:12.439 --> 00:01:13.599
"If you press it..."

00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:14.760
If you press it...

00:01:15.719 --> 00:01:16.719
"I'll go to save you."

00:01:17.319 --> 00:01:18.400
I'll go to save you.

00:01:36.159 --> 00:01:36.879
Why?

00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:40.159
Why do you pretend not to know me?

00:01:48.599 --> 00:01:49.400
I have my reasons.

00:01:51.079 --> 00:01:52.400
Is it because of the Wei family?

00:01:57.216 --> 00:01:58.599
Tell me!

00:02:00.920 --> 00:02:02.040
Gu Nian, listen to me.

00:02:02.640 --> 00:02:04.799
You must not
investigate this matter any further.

00:02:08.360 --> 00:02:10.439
You know the real culprit
behind all these murders.

00:02:11.639 --> 00:02:13.319
Yet, you choose to remain silent.

00:02:14.680 --> 00:02:16.960
You'd rather hurt me
to protect them, right?

00:02:16.960 --> 00:02:20.800
♪You overturned the story's ending♪

00:02:21.824 --> 00:02:23.800
♪Love ultimately becomes regret♪

00:02:23.800 --> 00:02:26.319
I thought you
had some genuine feelings for me.

00:02:28.120 --> 00:02:29.376
I guess I was wrong.

00:02:29.690 --> 00:02:32.760
♪Without your company♪

00:02:33.728 --> 00:02:35.840
We were never on the same side.

00:02:37.479 --> 00:02:38.280
Rest assured.

00:02:39.719 --> 00:02:42.039
I won't reveal your identity.

00:02:43.319 --> 00:02:44.879
Consider it repaying you for saving me.

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:47.680
I don't owe you anything anymore.

00:02:48.416 --> 00:02:50.429
♪Troubled time after time♪

00:02:51.479 --> 00:02:51.840
Gu Nian.

00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:52.319
Song Qian,

00:02:55.319 --> 00:02:56.960
I never want to see you again.

00:02:59.400 --> 00:03:00.639
Take it.

00:03:03.488 --> 00:03:04.080
Get lost.

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:10.272
♪I smile to hide the sorrows♪

00:03:10.496 --> 00:03:14.578
♪How long must regrets linger♪

00:03:14.578 --> 00:03:16.928
♪I calmly resist♪

00:03:16.928 --> 00:03:21.072
♪The loneliness when memories swarm♪

00:03:21.072 --> 00:03:24.096
♪But time often♪

00:03:24.398 --> 00:03:27.212
♪Makes me anxious♪

00:03:27.808 --> 00:03:32.160
♪A breeze chills my skin♪

00:03:32.448 --> 00:03:36.576
♪I weep while missing the past♪

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:40.532
♪Suppressing the urge to see you♪

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:43.252
♪Tears run wild♪

00:03:43.252 --> 00:03:47.384
♪Spreading into invisible wounds♪

00:03:47.384 --> 00:03:50.677
♪The dream hangs in mid-air♪

00:03:50.677 --> 00:03:53.862
♪Through the window I imagine♪

00:03:53.862 --> 00:04:00.627
♪The way you return♪

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:28.769
♪Cannot escape
the emotional entanglements♪

00:04:30.272 --> 00:04:32.608
♪Troubled time after time♪

00:04:32.890 --> 00:04:35.363
♪Filling up with tears♪

00:04:35.776 --> 00:04:39.422
♪My world turns dim♪

00:04:39.678 --> 00:04:42.578
♪I still can't learn to be brave♪

00:04:42.880 --> 00:04:48.127
♪I decide to wander♪

00:04:48.224 --> 00:04:52.291
♪I smile to hide the sorrows♪

00:04:52.484 --> 00:04:56.350
♪How long must regrets linger♪

