00:05:25.152 --> 00:05:29.303
♪Spreading into invisible wounds♪

00:05:29.303 --> 00:05:32.609
♪The dream hangs in mid-air♪

00:05:32.609 --> 00:05:35.688
♪Through the window I imagine♪

00:05:36.006 --> 00:05:42.307
♪The way you return♪

00:06:01.160 --> 00:06:02.720
(Looks like they came for the card.)

00:06:03.319 --> 00:06:04.759
(They got the news so fast.)

00:06:05.720 --> 00:06:06.959
(Could it be him?)

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:20.959
(I never want to see you again.)

00:06:35.759 --> 00:06:36.959
Hello, we're checking in.

00:06:37.399 --> 00:06:38.600
Two king rooms, please.

00:06:40.120 --> 00:06:41.839
Dr. Gu, what a coincidence!

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:44.199
Are you also here
for the medical seminar?

00:06:46.879 --> 00:06:48.199
Sorry, miss,

00:06:48.199 --> 00:06:50.199
but we only have
one king room available now.

00:06:54.199 --> 00:06:55.000
Qian,

00:06:55.360 --> 00:06:57.079
luckily we booked a suite.

00:06:57.079 --> 00:06:59.560
Otherwise, we'd be competing
with Dr. Gu.

00:07:03.560 --> 00:07:04.120
Senior,

00:07:04.839 --> 00:07:06.279
do you mind sharing a room with me?

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:08.680
Not at all.

00:07:10.519 --> 00:07:11.680
You're not a couple.

00:07:11.680 --> 00:07:13.000
It's improper to share a room.

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:14.079
Qian,

00:07:14.519 --> 00:07:16.600
how do you know they're not a couple?

00:07:16.920 --> 00:07:18.439
Sharing a room is quite normal.

00:07:21.759 --> 00:07:22.959
That's right, Mr. Song.

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:24.680
Aren't you a bit meddlesome?

00:07:29.480 --> 00:07:30.560
One king room, please.

00:07:32.519 --> 00:07:33.040
Thank you.

00:08:06.480 --> 00:08:08.279
(Impulsiveness is a devil, Gu Nian.)

00:08:14.959 --> 00:08:15.759
Nian,

00:08:16.279 --> 00:08:17.519
I'll take a shower.

00:08:18.639 --> 00:08:19.439
Okay.

00:08:34.879 --> 00:08:35.879
Hello, Weiwei?

00:08:36.759 --> 00:08:38.279
Did you open Zhou Shen's laptop?

00:08:38.720 --> 00:08:39.440
I did.

00:08:39.919 --> 00:08:41.480
But his office laptop is really clean.

00:08:41.840 --> 00:08:43.000
There's no Zhao Yan's record.

00:08:43.759 --> 00:08:44.720
Impossible.

00:08:53.341 --> 00:08:55.039
(Clinic Prescription)

00:08:55.039 --> 00:08:57.679
(The hospital prohibits
prescribing these drugs together.)

00:08:58.240 --> 00:08:59.480
(Why would Senior Zhou...?)

00:09:02.519 --> 00:09:03.320
(Zhao Yan?)

00:09:03.919 --> 00:09:04.840
(He knows Zhao Yan?)

00:09:05.480 --> 00:09:06.080
Nian?

00:09:07.960 --> 00:09:08.704
Why are you here?

00:09:12.200 --> 00:09:13.919
I wanted to invite you for lunch.

00:09:14.919 --> 00:09:15.440
Sure.

00:09:16.559 --> 00:09:18.080
What do you want to eat then?

00:09:18.679 --> 00:09:19.559
Anything works.

00:09:19.919 --> 00:09:20.320
Let's go.

00:09:26.279 --> 00:09:27.080
Wait a minute.

00:09:34.600 --> 00:09:35.759
He has a second laptop.

00:09:36.360 --> 00:09:37.720
Nian, be careful.

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:16.039
What are you doing?

00:10:17.519 --> 00:10:18.320
Nothing.

00:10:20.759 --> 00:10:21.639
Will you wash up?

00:10:31.960 --> 00:10:33.480
The seminar is about to start.

00:10:33.879 --> 00:10:35.159
I need to get ready.

00:10:35.159 --> 00:10:36.200
You go on ahead.

00:10:37.679 --> 00:10:38.720
I'll wait for you then.

00:10:42.240 --> 00:10:42.840
Nian,

00:10:44.399 --> 00:10:45.639
my patience is limited.

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:48.600
Don't make me wait too long.

00:11:03.600 --> 00:11:05.320
Mr. Song and Miss Wei
are a perfect couple.

00:11:05.480 --> 00:11:06.480
When's the wedding?

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:07.000
Soon.

00:11:07.960 --> 00:11:08.919
Don't drink too much.

00:11:09.159 --> 00:11:09.960
It's okay.

00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:13.312
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

00:11:19.639 --> 00:11:20.960
Long time no see.

00:11:37.718 --> 00:11:42.712
♪You overturned the story's ending♪

00:11:42.998 --> 00:11:46.807
♪Love ultimately becomes regret♪

00:11:48.639 --> 00:11:49.159
Everyone,

00:11:50.279 --> 00:11:52.399
I have an announcement to make.

00:11:53.360 --> 00:11:54.600
First, let me introduce

00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:56.840
my fiancé,

00:11:57.440 --> 00:11:58.279
Song Qian.

00:12:03.158 --> 00:12:08.456
♪Cannot escape
the emotional entanglements♪

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:10.120
What do you want to say?

00:12:12.399 --> 00:12:13.600
You'll know soon.

00:12:16.360 --> 00:12:17.159
Be patient.

00:12:20.799 --> 00:12:23.159
I want to share some good news
with everyone.

00:12:23.840 --> 00:12:25.600
Song Qian and I

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:27.399
are getting married next week.

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:30.759
Congratulations!

00:12:31.759 --> 00:12:32.679
How come I didn't know?

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:35.799
I wanted to surprise you.

00:12:35.990 --> 00:12:38.048
♪I calmly resist♪

00:12:38.262 --> 00:12:42.048
♪The loneliness when memories swarm♪

00:12:42.390 --> 00:12:45.324
♪But time often♪

00:12:45.590 --> 00:12:48.656
♪Makes me anxious♪

00:12:48.918 --> 00:12:53.476
♪A breeze chills my skin♪

00:12:54.120 --> 00:12:56.120
Wishing you a long and happy marriage.

00:12:57.782 --> 00:13:01.992
♪Suppressing the urge to see you♪

00:13:02.134 --> 00:13:04.392
♪Tears run wild♪

00:13:04.598 --> 00:13:08.305
♪Spreading into invisible wounds♪

00:13:08.470 --> 00:13:11.782
♪The dream hangs in mid-air♪

00:13:12.320 --> 00:13:12.799
Nian.

00:13:15.286 --> 00:13:22.072
♪The way you return♪

00:13:25.120 --> 00:13:25.919
Gu Nian.

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:29.840
We've known each other for so long.

00:13:30.039 --> 00:13:31.039
Won't you wish me well?

00:13:32.720 --> 00:13:34.320
Wishing you a happy wedding next week.

00:13:35.919 --> 00:13:37.159
How insincere.

00:13:38.200 --> 00:13:39.840
You asked me for my blessing.

00:13:40.480 --> 00:13:42.399
And now you call me insincere.

00:13:43.080 --> 00:13:44.840
You're really strange.

00:13:45.919 --> 00:13:48.240
Song Qian and I were happy.

00:13:48.759 --> 00:13:50.039
Ever since you showed up,

00:13:50.039 --> 00:13:51.240
everything has changed.

00:13:52.080 --> 00:13:54.200
You'd better keep a close eye
on Song Qian

00:13:55.399 --> 00:13:56.799
in case he falls for me.

00:13:57.759 --> 00:13:58.559
You...

00:14:02.320 --> 00:14:04.440
Don't show your spoiled attitude
in front of me.

00:14:05.240 --> 00:14:06.440
I'm not buying it.

00:14:22.039 --> 00:14:23.639
(Gu Nian, where are you?)

00:14:23.639 --> 00:14:24.840
(I'm waiting in the room.)

00:14:46.440 --> 00:14:47.480
What do you want?

00:14:49.360 --> 00:14:50.360
Why not answer my call?

00:14:50.840 --> 00:14:51.879
Why should I?

00:14:58.000 --> 00:15:00.039
Don't you want to ask about the wedding?

00:15:04.600 --> 00:15:05.080
No.

00:15:06.399 --> 00:15:07.399
Mr. Song,

00:15:07.399 --> 00:15:08.639
is there anything else?

00:15:10.320 --> 00:15:11.919
If not, I'll be leaving.

00:15:12.279 --> 00:15:13.039
Besides,

00:15:13.720 --> 00:15:15.039
Zhou Shen is waiting for me.

00:15:19.360 --> 00:15:20.360
I'll go back to my room.

00:15:37.000 --> 00:15:37.559
Gu Nian,

00:15:38.840 --> 00:15:39.919
Zhou Shen isn't the one.

00:15:40.919 --> 00:15:42.000
Then who is the one for me?

00:15:42.840 --> 00:15:43.320
You?

00:15:45.200 --> 00:15:47.360
Do you think I would be
with a drug dealer?

00:15:49.120 --> 00:15:49.759
Mr. Song,

00:15:50.720 --> 00:15:52.240
please get your facts straight.

00:15:53.159 --> 00:15:54.200
You have your fiancée.

00:15:54.200 --> 00:15:55.759
And I have my fiancé.

00:15:57.879 --> 00:15:59.000
Fiancé?

00:15:59.600 --> 00:16:00.720
What fiancé?

00:16:03.679 --> 00:16:05.320
I've already accepted his proposal.

00:16:08.080 --> 00:16:09.519
Do you know what you're doing?

00:16:09.519 --> 00:16:10.519
Of course, I do.

00:16:11.639 --> 00:16:13.600
You and Wei Qing
are getting married next week.

00:16:13.919 --> 00:16:15.919
Zhou Shen and I
are also getting married soon.

00:16:16.720 --> 00:16:18.840
There's nothing between us anymore.

00:16:21.759 --> 00:16:22.960
What do you mean by nothing?

00:16:24.840 --> 00:16:26.039
You said you loved me.

00:16:26.039 --> 00:16:27.039
That was in the past.

00:16:30.639 --> 00:16:32.240
Now, whether you're K

00:16:33.080 --> 00:16:34.919
or Song Qian,

00:16:35.279 --> 00:16:36.799
I won't love you anymore.

00:16:58.639 --> 00:16:59.240
Nian.

00:17:38.038 --> 00:17:42.573
♪What is secretly stirring♪

00:17:43.862 --> 00:17:48.249
♪From your mouth,
I find it hard to describe♪

00:17:49.462 --> 00:17:54.013
♪What praises can disappear
in just a second♪

00:17:54.294 --> 00:18:00.448
♪Vanishing without a trace♪

00:18:00.918 --> 00:18:06.048
♪Waving hands to break free
from the splendid cage♪

00:18:06.518 --> 00:18:11.939
♪Words against the heart,
a pain slashes through the sky♪

00:18:12.150 --> 00:18:16.736
♪Floating into the endless night sky,
the wind fierce and strong♪

00:18:17.078 --> 00:18:23.901
♪Who is reckless, continuing
to lose control, with impunity♪

00:18:25.686 --> 00:18:31.278
♪Let me disappear into the darkness♪

00:18:31.510 --> 00:18:36.772
♪Cannot see
who is pulling the strings behind♪

00:18:37.174 --> 00:18:41.617
♪The wound still aches,
and the memory is not yet over♪

00:18:41.846 --> 00:18:48.139
♪There are two endings,
whether you understand or not♪

00:18:48.374 --> 00:18:53.744
♪Let me disappear into the darkness♪

00:18:53.974 --> 00:18:59.305
♪Cannot see who is tracking from behind♪

00:18:59.606 --> 00:19:04.256
♪The heart still beats,
total blood-red before my eyes♪

00:19:04.534 --> 00:19:10.445
♪Only one ending remains,
whether it helps or not♪

00:19:10.934 --> 00:19:16.630
♪Let me disappear into the darkness♪